around for 5 years, 10 years,

00:48:37.969 --> 00:48:40.260
instead of just building a
game to be around for a year

00:48:40.260 --> 00:48:43.984
is going to be huge
for the future.

00:48:43.984 --> 00:48:46.400
LLOYD TULLUES: I've been in
